a6dab64bb532a9d57","tid":2328031,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"中二病..."},{"pid":"7e2981f7dac78e5271d7339b91a2cebc903d71b5","tid":2328031,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efc845d39c48f64e299ebe1e8a270c05e4f9b384","tid":2328031,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f623bda5ea5e943ec9d98b52187c8eac73764ce1","tid":2328031,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"482a09f73fcc0ea55abcfd482603ce1961ad81d4","tid":2328031,"uid":340088,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"係就777 啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"可能已經寫咗病死，但唔記得指定死亡時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今天係奇拿吸取教訓之後試驗武肺可唔可以指定時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"只可以13日內<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:12:51.000Z","msg":"60、在死亡筆記本寫上病死，且指定病名與時間的情況下，假設所指定的時間與疾病進行速度出現矛盾，則犧牲者將在寫完40秒之後心臟麻痺而死。<br />\n<br />\n61、寫上病死，未寫明病名但指定時間的情況下，犧牲者將在預定的時間內死於適當的疾病。不過，死亡筆記本能夠操縱的死亡時間僅限於人間界單位的23天以內。<br />\n<br />\n二十八<br />\n<br />\n62、寫上病死，寫出病名但沒有指定時間的情況下，假設該病情發展需要24天以上的時間，就會違反「操縱死亡時間須於23天以內」的規則。犧牲者將在適當的時間死於指定的疾病。<br />\n<br />\n係23日內，如果係寫武肺，23內夠哂病情發展需要嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e111756a7fb7f53ec9f8aad09b11e932d6ec88","tid":2328031,"uid":363330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:15:45.000Z","msg":"真係有奇拿<br />\n制裁呢啲蝦兵蟹將有鬼用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細細地都起碼滅河妖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a173b4fe5443770a1a8a11bfbac16e9daedbaeeb","tid":2328031,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4e111756a7fb7f53ec9f8aad09b11e932d6ec88","tid":2328031,"uid":363330,"lik